title: Did Budesta Clinton say she had an Odor Cage, which used a false term for developmental disability?
subtitle: There's an allegedly fabricated document from WikiLeaks 'E-mails Budista' that describes Hillary Clinton as acting foolishly and smells like cabbage.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: The WikiLeaks documents have revealed that campaign leader John Bodista has indifferently described Hillary Clinton's personal health and thought.
